text:
“Next round kon kon piyega”
Bhai Idk kaise itni capacity hai teri but kisi din toh tereko pura bhand krunga. 
Promise.

Tere ghar itni trips maar li hain ki now it feels like apna hi ghar hai xD. You are one of the most sincere guys I’ve ever met. Antaragni krna, acads mein chaapna aur hame (Mujhe and Aakarsh) ko roz practice ke liye uthana bhi. Teri sincerity kabhi bhi irritate bhi kr deti hai lekin seh lenge thoda. Apan ko bas tere ladkiyon ke taste pe kaam krna hai thoda xD. Baaki I’m still jealous of your smile. 

“Apan toh milte hi rhenge”
author: Pragyan  Pandey
